【体貌篇】

五官

a round face 圆脸

a pointed face 尖下巴脸型

an oval ['əʊv(ə)l] face 鹅蛋脸

a straight nose 很直很挺的鼻子

an upturned nose 翘翘的鼻子

a droopy没精神地下垂的 ['druːpɪ] moustache 小胡子 [mə'stɑːʃ]

bushy eyebrows 浓密的眉毛

chubby胖的可爱的['tʃʌbɪ] cheeks 面颊[tʃiːk]


面容

sb. have a lovely complexion [kəm'plekʃ(ə)n] 气色、肤质

sb. have a striking [ˈstraɪkɪŋ] appearance 非常引人注目的容颜

sb. have a dazzling十分吸引人的['dæzlɪŋ] smile 迷人的笑容

sb. don't look one's age 看着比实际年龄年轻


身材

sb. have a slim figure 苗条的身材

sb. have a slender waist纤细的腰身

sb. be well-built 身材很好

sb. have broad shoulders 宽厚的肩膀

a woman is dumpy [ˈdʌmpi] (short and quite fat)

a man is portly [ˈpɔːtli] (fat and round)

a young man is lanky [ˈlæŋki] (tall and thin)


头发

sb. have sleek 光滑明亮 [sliːk], shoulder-length hair. 光亮齐肩短发

sb. have thick hair 浓密的头发

jet-black 纯黑色的 hair

fair hair 金发

ginger ['dʒɪndʒə] hair 姜黄色头发


