【性格篇】

靠谱

sb. have a strong/great/good sense of responsibility 有强烈的责任感

sb. always keep one's word 信守承诺

sb. be good at keeping secrets 秘密['siːkrɪt] 善于保守秘密

sb. be fiercely 强烈地 ['fɪəslɪ] loyal忠实的['lɒɪəl] to sb. 对某人非常的忠诚

sb. always put others first 总是把别人放在首位

sb. be an upright person 正直的人

sb. can preserve保护 one's integrity 正直诚实 [in'teɡrəti] 恪守自己正直诚实的品性


脾气好

sb. can keep one's temper 脾气['tempə] all the time 脾气一直都很好

sb. be a good company 是一个好伙伴

sb. never lose one's temper/patience 从不发脾气 / 从不失去耐心

sb. can come to terms with sth. 心理上接受了某个不好的事情

    Eventually [ɪˈventʃuəli] 最终, he came to terms with that fact that he failed to pass the exam. - 最终，他在心理上接受了他考试没有通过的事实。 

sb. be an easy person to work/study with 工作/学习方面好相处的人

sb. always give everyone a warm, friendly smile 总是给人温暖友好的微笑

sb. never hurt one's feeling(s) 从不会伤害别人的感受

sb. swallow下咽 ['swɒləʊ] one's pride 放下他的自尊心

sb. have an outgoing personality 拥有外向的性格

sb. never bear a grudge 怨恨 [grʌdʒ] against sth. / sb. 对某事或某人心怀怨恨


脾气差

sb. be full of pent-up被压抑的 anger towards sth. 压抑着针对…的愤怒

Politeness is not one's strong point. 礼貌不是他的长项

sb. have an abrasive粗鲁的 [ə'breɪsɪv] manner 有着粗鲁的举止


精力旺盛

sb. have boundless [ˈbaʊndləs] 无边的 energy 精力无限

sb. is bursting ['bə:stiŋ] 充满的 with energy 精力充沛

sb. can boost [buːst] 激发 one's confidence 能够激发某人的自信

sb. don't act one's age 举止与年龄不符

Sb. don’t look one's age 比实际年龄看起来年轻


自私

sb. have a selfish [ˈselfɪʃ] streak [striːk] 有自私的个性


固执、直率

sb. have a stubborn ['stʌbən] 固执的 streak 有固执的个性

sb. have a forthright [,fɔ:θ'rait] 直率的 manner 直率的行为方式


开心、快乐

sb. have a strong/great/good sense of humour [ˈhjuːmə(r)] 很有幽默感

sb. have a wonderful and bubbly ['bʌblɪ] 快活热情的 personality. 有着特别好的快活热情的性格


聪明

sb. have a vivid [ˈvɪvɪd] 鲜活的 imagination [ɪˌmædʒɪˈneɪʃn] 拥有丰富的想象力

sb. is highly intelligent [ɪn'telɪdʒ(ə)nt] 非常聪明

sb. have a tendency [ˈtendənsi] 趋势 to make snap [snæp] 迅速的 decisions 倾向于当机立断

sb. have a razor ['reɪzə]剃刀-sharp wit [wɪt] .非常聪明智慧

sb. be versatile ['və:sətail] 多才多艺的

sb. be artistic [ɑːˈtɪstɪk] 有艺术才能的

sb. be a consummate [ˈkɒnsəˌmeɪt] 技术精湛的 actor / singer/ leader


善于工作

sb. be determined 意志坚定的 and self-reliant [rɪˈlaɪənt] 自立的

sb. be a self-made man / woman 靠自身努力成功的人

sb. can show initiative [ɪ'nɪʃətɪv] 主动性

sb. be tenacious [tɪ'neɪʃəs] 执着的

sb. have great willpower 意志力

sb. have set the benchmark [ˈbentʃmɑːk] 标杆 for sth. 某人为…（通常指某行业）树立了标杆

sb. be a go-getter采取行动取得成功的人


有名

sb. be world-renowned [rɪˈnaʊnd] 闻名于世

sb. have a large following [ˈfɒləʊɪŋ] 有大批粉丝
