如何描述住处

    this is my dream home 梦中之家

    it's a four- storey [ˈstɔːri] house 四层别墅

    It's got a spacious [ˈspeɪʃəs] living room宽敞的客厅 which has a wonderful view of the park能看到公园

    There are many airy [ˈeəri] bedrooms空气流通很好的卧室 which can overlook俯瞰 the garden of my house. 


各式建筑物

    the building is still under construction [kənˈstrʌkʃn] 还在建的建筑

